data.meta_description: Pauline Koch was born in the year 1858 in Cannstadt., they had 3 children. She died in the year 1920 in Germany. This information is part of McDonald and Potts family tree- black Jewish YAHYA family line 2 by Dr Wilton McDonald- black Hebrew on Genealogy Online.
